{
  "stem": "10905.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I also saw other films thinking that all of the United States was noontime down on Wall Street area, with thousands of people walking.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These were the preceptions that I had coming to the United States, obviously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we moved to Queens, one and two-family-- one and two-story buildings.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, totally, totally, totally different when we came here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We stayed in the Bronx for three days, the first three days with some friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we moved to Queens in three days after we'd been here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, of course, I started school again, and this time I started in English.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a lot of problems.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In those days, young boys didn't wear slacks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wore shorts-- wore shorts in the summertime, wore shorts in the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, only sissies wear shorts here, or so it seems in 1947.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was in a fight every day for the first couple months that I was in school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But by that time, I spoke pretty good English quite well, because we came in July, and school started in September.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in two months, you know, I managed to get a working vocabulary and speak the language relatively well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, it was, it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father-- well, firstly, my father, being a professional, he had to take a-- learn English.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a special English for-- examination you had to pass as a foreign professional.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once you pass that before, then you could first study and take an examination for your specialty, if you were a physician or dentist or attorney, what have you.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very, very difficult for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My mother had been a prima donna, the daughter of very, very wealthy, as I told you, very, very wealthy parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
